Titolo: Xenoblade Chronicles 2: Torna – The Golden Country

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Xenoblade Chronicles 2: Torna – The Golden Country is an open world action role-playing video game developed by Monolith Soft and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch console. It is a story expansion to the 2017 game, Xenoblade Chronicles 2, and was released both as downloadable content and as a standalone title.